🌎 Myodetox 2023 Innovation Retreat 🌎 
.
Last week was an unforgettable experience and point of reflection of my time at @myodetox 
.
To be surrounded by so many likeminded and talented people is an incredibly motivating and powerful experience. Our support hub and Clinic Directors came together to discuss our experiences, challenge ourselves, and ultimately grow to better serve our teams and respective communities. 
.
I am so honoured and thankful to be a part of this growing team ( I couldn’t tag everyone 😭) and the truly positive change we aim to make in the world. 🚀
.
Many more pages to add to this amazing story. Cheers to #TheNext100 pages 🥂👀
.

✌️ TWO YEARS OLD ✌️ 
.
It’s hard to believe that @myodetox PATH is officially 2 years old 🤯 
.
We have such a passionate and talented team (which continues to grow) that I’m incredibly proud of. We’ve consistently strive to make a positive impact on the downtown Toronto community and I can confidently say that we are fulfilling the mission and vision of the Myodetox. 🚀

I’ve learned so much from each and every person on this team who’s continues to fuel my passion for growth every single day. It’s been an absolute pleasure growing this clinic and we’re truly just getting started!
.
There may be a couple surprises on the way too 😏
.
(Missing a few important team members from this photo! 🥹 , tagged you all 💜)
.
Cheers to the next year of growth with this incredible team 🥂
.
.

🥂TWENTY SEVEN 🥂 
.
Happiest of birthdays to the most important person in my life. @nicole_gregory , you are truly one of a kind in this crazy and wild world. 🌎 
.
This weekend will be one for the books. I cannot wait to celebrate your birthday as well as our engagement with friends and family 💕 
.
Also had to flashback to Jamaica since we’re going back. 😎
.
Cheers to you today babe 🥂

Anything is possible when you have the right people there to support you. 
.
Feeling very thankful today for all the incredible support from our friends and family last weekend at our engagement party. ❤️

Happy Fathers Day to all the special Dads out there - the guiding light that shines through every step of life.
.
Today’s for you 🥂
.
📸The Hart Boys, mid 1990’s

Love is composed of a single soul inhabiting two bodies. I know it sounds cliche, but at a certain point you just know you were meant to find each other. 💕
.
The future Harts @nicole_gregory

Had a great weekend with friends and family celebrating the marriage of Morgan and Lawrence. 

Congrats to the newlyweds 🥂

🥂 Our Special Day 🥂
.
Today is the day I get the privilege to marry my best friend on this planet. @nicole_gregory you’ve been nothing but amazing since the moment I met you. 
.
The most valuable commodity on this planet is most definitely time. Time is the one thing we will never get back. When it’s spent, it’s spent. We choose how we spend it, and I’m so happy that I get to spend it with you. With that, we create memories. We have so many memories that will outlast the present time and will live on. 
.
This video is a collection of some of the most special times spent together over the last four years of our lives. They’re memories - a glimpse into that “spent time”, a gift into the past and an indication of the fun we will have together in the future. 

Cheers to us, on our day and for the rest of them to come ❤️
.
She’s Finally, Mine 🎶
Woke up as husband & wife on our 4 year anniversary yesterday. 🤍 What a way to celebrate being together for 4 years! 🤍💍

We did it 💍

Thank you to all our amazing friends, family and vendors for helping this day come together! We couldn’t do this without you! 

xoxo

🥂Myodetox Toronto Leadership Team! 🥂
.
Last Friday we had the privilege to reflect and celebrate an amazing year of growth for the @myodetox Toronto region after the pandemic. We opened two new locations ( Liberty and Sauga) with  Leslieville already announced for next year. 
.
We also made a special announcement of more to come in 2024, stay tuned! 👀
.

Hey Google… Play 2023 on repeat 🥹 🎶
.
This post certainly does not do the last year justice. These are just a few highlights over the last year, six weddings, four bachelor parties, a couple babies welcomed to the family, and some amazing professional experiences with Myodetox. 
.
Thank you to each and every person who has been a part of the last year with @nicole_gregory and myself. Your support has been so appreciated as we officially tied the knot this year 🥂❤️ 
.
The next year will be another chapter in what I’m blessed to call life. More weddings ( 🇯🇲 let’s goo!) traveling the world, the PATH clinic expansion, and returning to school (UWO) to take the next step in the physiotherapy profession… just to name a few. 
.
There was some well deserved R&R over the holidays, but I’m more than ready more than ever to get back to it and tackle 2024 full force. This time, with my best friend by my side for life ❤️
.
Let’s go 🚀
